---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Midjourney vs DALL-E 4：AI绘画工具谁更强 - Fidu Tools">
  <article style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto">
    <div style="margin-bottom:2rem">
      <span style="display:inline-block;background:#eef2ff;color:var(--primary);padding:0.25rem 0.75rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:0.85rem">AI图像生成</span>
      <h1 style="font-size:2rem;margin:1rem 0 0.5rem">Midjourney vs DALL-E 4：AI绘画工具谁更强</h1>
      <p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.9rem">2026年6月更新</p>
    </div>

    <div style="background:#f0f9ff;border:1px solid #bae6fd;border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1rem 1.25rem;margin-bottom:2rem;font-size:0.9rem">
      <strong>快速选择：</strong>追求艺术感和视觉风格 → 选 <a href="#" style="color:var(--primary)">Midjourney</a>；需要精准控制和文字理解 → 选 <a href="#" style="color:var(--primary)">DALL-E 4</a>。
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.4rem;margin:2rem 0 1rem">直接购买</h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem">
      <div style="border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1.25rem;text-align:center">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem">Midjourney 标准版</h3>
        <p style="font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--primary)">/月</p>
        <a href="#" style="display:inline-block;margin-top:1rem;background:var(--primary);color:#fff;padding:0.5rem 1.5rem;border-radius:999px;text-decoration:none;font-size:0.9rem">立即体验 →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1.25rem;text-align:center">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem">ChatGPT (含DALL-E)</h3>
        <p style="font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--primary)">/月</p>
        <a href="#" style="display:inline-block;margin-top:1rem;background:var(--primary);color:#fff;padding:0.5rem 1.5rem;border-radius:999px;text-decoration:none;font-size:0.9rem">立即使用 →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p>更多详细评测内容即将上线，敬请期待...</p>
  </article>
</Base>
